+;# Alpha OpenVMS trampoline
+;#
+	.set noreorder
+	.set volatile
+	.set noat
+	.file 1 "vms_tramp.asm"
+.text
+	.align 3
+	.globl __tramp
+	.ent __tramp
+__tramp..en:
+
+.link
+	.align 3
+__tramp:
+	.pdesc __tramp..en,null
+.text
+	ldq $1,24($27)
+	ldq $27,16($27)
+	ldq $28,8($27)
+	jmp $31,($28),0
+	.end __tramp
